  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-07-29",
    "date": "2022-08-15T17:26:07Z",
    "text": "No Tax Deductions for Workplace Harasser Buyouts Act\n\nThis bill modifies the tax deduction for trade or business expenses to deny a deduction for payments made to any employee in connection with the termination of employment if a factor in the termination was sexual assault, sexual harassment, sexual misconduct, or workplace harassment based on race, color, national origin, religion, sex, disability, or other specified factors."
  },
